      "rationale": "All nonlinear quasi-static analyses converged to force and displacement residuals below 1e-7. Energy balance monitored across all 20 load increments; maximum error 0.06%. Solver error contribution to total uncertainty estimated at <0.5% of QoI magnitude."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent analyst review of model setup, boundary conditions, and post-processing scripts prior to result extraction.",
      "rationale": "A second FDA analyst independently reviewed the Ansys Mechanical project file, boundary condition assignments, and Python post-processing scripts against the simulation plan. Three minor discrepancies in load application reference frame were identified and corrected before final runs. No residual use errors identified."
